<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>

<section xml:id="sec-changes-of-coordinates">
  <title>Changes of coordinates</title>

  <objectives>
    <ol>
      <li>
        <p>
          Use coordinate changes to recast a problem in a more convenient frame of reference.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Express relationships between variables in new coordinates and observe how familiar equations transform.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          Work with polar coordinates to describe curves and regions that are difficult to express in rectangular form.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </objectives>
  
  <introduction>
    <p>
      Introduction goes here.
    </p>
  </introduction>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <p>
        Frame this in terms of choosing a change of variables that makes it easier to represent a problem.
        It's all about finding the right frame of reference.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</section>
